Create shaded RGB version of our raster DEM. Colors will be taken from the current symbology and shading will be done according to selected shading mode.
Cruise Tools offers three multiplication based shading modes:
[ Hillshade ]
Shading by synthetic light source, 315° Azimuth, 45° Altitude.
[ Slope ]
Shading by stretched slope inclination.
[ Combo ]
Shading by a combination of the two, bringing together the best aspects of both methods. Also widely known as "Simon's magical relief visualization"